==Bundles==
Fairy Rose is one of the options for the {{Bundle|garden||y}}

==Tailoring==
Fairy Rose can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Long Dress]].  [[File:Long Dress.png|36px]] The fairy rose can also be used as a red dye pot color for [[dyeing]], located in [[2 Willow Lane]], [[Emily]] and [[Haley]]'s house.

==Quests==
Fairy Rose is not used in any [[quests]].

==Notes==
*Fairy Roses have an equal chance of being one of six different colors. Fairy Roses of different colors will occupy different slots in inventory or chests. Six colors &times; four [[Crops#Crop Quality|quality]] levels = 24 possible spaces used.
:[[File:FairyRoseColors.png]]

*Despite not having a true red variation, Fairy Roses are used as a red dye in the dye pots.
*Despite the description, Fairy Roses do not have any effect on the [[Random Events#The Crop Fairy|the Crop Fairy event]].

